metadata.name: DREAMS
metadata.description:
Paralyzing emotions. One step forward and suddenly, without warning, everything changes. I find surprises, gifts and anguish. The road continues unleashing adventures.✨🌈

I’m finally able to run, now I think: Will I be able to fly?🐛🦋


Believe your dream is not a coincidence.
Your dream is who you are.😉💫💕
